title: Introducing the etnies Marana with Ryan Sheckler
description:
etni.es/introducingthemarana
Introducing Ryan Sheckler's etnies Marana. Featuring an STI Evolution™ Foam midsole, STI Non-slip grip outsole, specialized polyurethane footbed and reinforced rubber toe cap, the etnies Marana is, in Ryan's own words, "the best jumping shoe I've ever had." Hear for yourself how Ryan designed his latest signature shoe for durability and style.
See full product details and enter to win your own pair at etnies.com/shop/marana/red/
More footage, photos and exclusive Ryan Sheckler interview at etni.es/sheckler-marana
